Then: & Security

All processing happens locally on your computer:
- ‚úÖ No cloud uploads
- ‚úÖ No API calls to external services (except HuggingFace token for diarization)
- ‚úÖ Your data never leaves your computer
- ‚úÖ No telemetry or tracking
- ‚úÖ Works completely offline
- ‚úÖ Open source - code is auditable
