- [Troubleshooting]

### "LLM model not found" error
- Download a GGUF model to `models/` directory
- Default expected: `models/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-Q4_K_M.gguf`
- Or set `OPENMEET_LLM_MODEL=your-model.gguf` environment variable

### "Whisper executable not found"
- Rebuild whisper.cpp: `cd whisper.cpp && mkdir build && cd build && cmake .. && cmake --build . --config Release`

### Audio capture issues
- Check audio device: `python -c "import sounddevice; print(sounddevice.query_devices())"`
- Set device index: `OPENMEET_AUDIO_DEVICE_INDEX=<number>`

### Settings not persisting
- Check location:
  - **macOS/Linux:** `~/Library/Application Support/OpenMeet/data/settings.json` or `~/.local/share/OpenMeet/data/settings.json`
  - **Windows:** `%APPDATA%\OpenMeet\data\settings.json`

